'''''Challenge'' 57''' was a roleplaying magazine from February of [[1992]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[Green Squad 3 (article)|Green Squad 3]]" and was written by [[Stephen A. Marinaccio]].

